The paper proposes a machine learning approach for predicting drug-drug interactions based on multiple data sources and uses embedding techniques and convolutional LSTM networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) due to the use of ML techniques, Databases (cs.DB) due to the use of multiple data sources, Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) due to the use of natural language processing techniques, and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) due to the potential applications in the medical field.
